## About BiasNeutralizer

BiasNeutralizer is a browser extension that leverages Chrome's Built-in AI APIs
(Prompt API, Summarizer API, and Rewriter API) to detect and highlight media
bias in news articles in real-time. This project was created to promote media
literacy and help readers critically evaluate news content.

### Powered By
- Chrome Built-in AI: Prompt API
- Chrome Built-in AI: Summarizer API
- Chrome Built-in AI: Rewriter API

### Attribution
This project uses Chrome's experimental AI APIs. The AI models and APIs are
provided by Google Chrome and are subject to their own terms and conditions.
